                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If the vilderavn kills a humanoid with a critical hit using their jaws Strike, they rip out and devour the target's heart and soul as part of the attack.</p>\n<p>While the target is dead, the vilderavn can Change Shape into the target's form, gaining a +4 status bonus to Deception checks to impersonate the target.</p>\n<p>If magic would resurrect the creature, the caster must succeed at a DC 34 counteract check to extract the target's soul from the vilderavn; otherwise, the spell fails.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "ORC",
